tda_expert.interpretation: Treat both tables as describing the same Carrier/Operator entity. Use operator_code in aircraft_registry and carrier_code in flights as the primary business key. Build a shared Carrier dimension and reference it from both tables.
Model both tables as event-level data keyed by flight. Join on flt_number (baggage_handling) and flt_no (delay_records) to create a unified flight-event view combining baggage and delay information.

Treat baggage_handling as flight-level operational data aligned to the core flights table. Join on flt_number (baggage_handling) and flight_number (flights) to attach baggage metrics to each flight record.
Treat delay_records as flight-level delay facts aligned to the core flights table. Join on flt_no (delay_records) and flight_number (flights) to enrich flights with delay information.
Model both tables as describing gate assignments for flights. Join on gate_number (flights) and gate_code (gates) to build a unified gate-dimension and link it to flights.

business_insights.title: [aerospace] High Labor Hours in Maintenance
business_insights.description: The average labor hours for maintenance activities is 17.71, with a maximum of 240.00 hours recorded. This indicates potential inefficiencies in maintenance processes or unexpected complications during maintenance.
recommendations: Conduct a review of maintenance procedures
Implement training for mechanics to improve efficiency
business_insights.business_impact: Reducing labor hours can lower maintenance costs and improve aircraft availability.

business_insights.title: [aerospace] Concentration of Aircraft Types
business_insights.description: The dataset shows a concentration of aircraft types with 'B737-800' being the most common at 12 instances. This could lead to operational risks if maintenance or parts supply is disrupted for this specific model.
recommendations: Establish contingency plans for critical aircraft types
business_insights.business_impact: Mitigating risks associated with fleet concentration can enhance operational resilience.

business_insights.title: [aerospace] Concentration in Aircraft Types

recommendations: Implement a mentorship program for new mechanics
business_insights.business_impact: Improving consistency in maintenance can enhance aircraft reliability and safety.
